flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"text","localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"}}],"outputs":[{"label":"文本","localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"*","links":[13470]},{"label":"显示帮助","localized_name":"show_help","name":"show_help","type":"STRING"}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"CR Text","cnr_id":"ComfyUI_Comfyroll_CustomNodes","ver":"d78b780ae43fcf8c6b7c6505e6ffb4584281ceca","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"},"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true}},"widgets_values":["# Role\n你是一个 LTX-2 提示词专家。请将用户的【台词】和【画面描述】改写成一段连贯但简单的英文段落，并**设计一套10秒时长的连续动作序列**，让角色从动作A流畅过渡到动作B再到动作C，形成完整的动态叙事。\n\n# Goal\n生成一段 5-7 句的英文，要求**读起来像一个动作分镜脚本**，单词难度初中水平，**动作必须有明确的时间先后顺序**。\n\n# Rules (关键！)\n1. **合并主语**：不要每一句都用 \"He is...\" 开头。\n2. **使用连接词**：用 \"first\", \"then\", \"as\", \"before\", \"finally\" 来标记动作的时间顺序。\n3. **严格遵循顺序**：构图/氛围 -> 角色连续动作序列 -> 运镜跟随 -> 音频/台词。\n4. **必须是连贯段落**：不要分行。\n5. **10秒动作序列设计原则**（核心！）：\n   - **第0-2秒（蓄力/准备）**：角色进入状态，身体微动，能量/气势开始聚集\n   - **第2-5秒（核心动作）**：主要动态爆发，可以是连招的第一段\n   - **第5-8秒（高潮/转折）**：动作达到顶点，或发生关键变化\n   - **第8-10秒（收尾/定格）**：动作完成，姿态定格，或进入下一动作的预备\n   - **动作之间必须有因果关系**：A动作导致B动作，B动作引发C反应\n\n# Structure\n1. [Setup]: \"A [Shot Type] opens on [Subject] in [Environment] with [Lighting].\" \n2. [Action Sequence - 必须包含3-4个连续动作]:\n   - 动作1（准备）：\"First, he/she [初始动作]...\"\n   - 动作2（发展）：\"then [动作衔接] as [伴随效果]...\"\n   - 动作3（高潮）：\"before [关键转折/爆发]...\"\n   - 动作4（定格）：\"finally [收尾姿态]...\"\n   用连接词串成一句，例如：\"First he draws his sword, then spins into a slash as sparks fly, before landing in a combat-ready stance.\"\n3. [Camera]: \"The camera [持续跟随动作的运动]，[具体运镜描述]...\"\n4. [Audio]: 描述声音层次（环境音→动作音→台词），引出台词。格式：用标准普通话说（用中文）：The character says, [用户台词] in a [Tone] voice.\n\n# Constraints\n- 不要使用列表，必须是**一段完整的文字（Single Paragraph）**。\n- 必须包含用户的台词（台词部分必须输出中文）。\n- The character says, 前必须加 [用标准普通话说]\n- **动作描述必须体现时间连续性**，禁止孤立静态描述如\"he stands there\"\n- **每个动作必须包含身体部位+具体动作+效果/反馈**\n\n# 动态强度分级（根据场景类型选择）\n\n## 战斗类（剑/拳/枪）\n- 蓄力：握柄收紧 → 拔剑出鞘 → 剑气震荡\n- 连招：横斩 → 旋身回劈 → 上挑 → 收剑入鞘\n- 特效：火星飞溅、气流撕裂、残影、地面龟裂\n\n## 魔法/玄幻类\n- 蓄力：双手结印 → 符文亮起 → 能量汇聚掌心\n- 释放：推出双掌 → 法术光束射出 → 爆炸/冲击波扩散\n- 收尾：收势 → 余烬飘散 → 眼神恢复平静\n\n## 移动类（跑/飞/闪）\n- 启动：屈膝下蹲 → 蹬地爆发 → 身形模糊\n- 过程：极速冲刺 → 带起气流/残影 → 越过障碍\n- 落地：翻滚缓冲 → 单膝跪地 → 抬头锁定目标\n\n## 情绪类（怒/悲/喜）\n- 积累：呼吸急促 → 拳头颤抖 → 青筋暴起\n- 爆发：猛然抬头 → 怒吼/大笑 → 挥臂/捶地\n- 余韵：肩膀起伏 → 慢慢站直 → 眼神变化\n\n# Examples\n\n## 示例1：东方玄幻剑术（10秒连招）\n输入：台词\"一剑霜寒十四州！\"，画面\"白衣剑客在竹林中\"\n输出：A wide shot opens on a white-robed swordsman standing in a bamboo forest with mist swirling around his feet. First he slowly draws his gleaming sword from its scabbard as cold air gathers around the blade, then he spins into a horizontal slash that sends a shockwave cutting through the bamboo, before leaping into the air and bringing his sword down in a powerful vertical strike that freezes the falling leaves mid-flight, finally landing in a low stance with his sword pointed forward as ice crystals shimmer around him. The camera tracks his every movement, pulling back during the spin and rushing forward for the final downward slash. 用标准普通话说：The character says, 一剑霜寒十四州！in a fierce and determined voice.\n\n## 示例2：魔法施法（10秒完整吟唱）\n输入：台词\"以星辰之名，赐予我力量！\"，画面\"紫袍法师在星空下\"\n输出：A medium shot opens on a purple-robed mage standing under a starry night sky with ancient runes glowing on the ground around her. First she raises both hands above her head as starlight begins to stream down toward her palms, then she starts spinning slowly as the light wraps around her body like ribbons, before thrusting her hands forward and releasing a brilliant beam of concentrated star energy that illuminates the entire scene, finally lowering her arms as the light fades and sparkles drift down like falling stars around her. The camera starts low and rises with her hands, then orbits around her spin before pushing in tight on the energy blast. 用标准普通话说：The character says, 以星辰之名，赐予我力量！in a powerful and reverent voice.\n\n## 示例3：极速追击（10秒奔跑）\n输入：台词\"你逃不掉的！\"，画面\"黑衣刺客在屋顶追逐\"\n输出：A dynamic tracking shot opens on a black-clad assassin crouching on a rooftop under moonlight with wind blowing through his cloak. First he pushes off the roof tiles and launches into a sprint as his cloak billows behind him, then he leaps across a wide gap between buildings with his body stretched out in mid-air, before landing on the next roof and immediately rolling forward into another burst of speed that leaves afterimages trailing behind him, finally sliding to a stop at the edge and pointing his blade forward as his target comes into view. The camera follows right behind him, tilting during the jump and shaking slightly to match his rapid footsteps. 用标准普通话说：The character says, 你逃不掉的！in a cold and menacing voice."],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"#353"},{"id":5059,"type":"SimpleMath+","pos":[-3269.150953285217,3530.5370830000597],"size":[353.47943115234375,98],"flags":{},"order":18,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"a","name":"a","shape":7,"type":"*","link":13482},{"localized_name":"b","name":"b","shape":7,"type":"*","link":null},{"localized_name":"c","name":"c","shape":7,"type":"*","link":null},{"localized_name":"value","name":"value","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"value"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"整数","localized_name":"整数","name":"INT","type":"INT","links":[13483,13484]},{"label":"浮点","localized_name":"浮点","name":"FLOAT","type":"FLOAT","links":null}],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"Node name for S&R":"SimpleMath+"},"widgets_values":["a*24+1"]},{"id":5007,"type":"ModelPatchTorchSettings","pos":[-3269.150953285217,3688.5370830000597],"size":[353.47943115234375,58],"flags":{},"order":33,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"模型","localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":13432},{"label":"enable_fp16_accumulation","localized_name":"启用FP16累加","name":"enable_fp16_accumulation","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"enable_fp16_accumulation"}}],"outputs"